These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, poker, monopoly, canasta
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, librarian, pilot, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, spanish, turkish
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hamster, mouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, january, october
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, chaman, game, blend
 1. the turkish is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is not the chaman-smoker##6
 4. the game-smoker is not the person playing poker##6
 5. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 7. the blend-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
 8. the japanese is the coach##1
 9. the pilot is not the person playing canasta##6
10. the videographer is the chaman-smoker##1
11. the pilot is the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
13. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
15. the polish is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
16. the game-smoker is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the blend-smoker##7
17. the person who's birthday is in october is not the japanese##6
18. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
19. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the coach and the person who's birthday is in march##7
20. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person playing canasta##6
21. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Game          | chess      | canasta   | poker     | monopoly |
| Job           | videographer | librarian   | coach    | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | time-travel | horror   | mystery   |
| Nationality   | spanish      | turkish     | japanese | polish    |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | mouse       | hamster  | cat       |
| Birthday         | march     | august     | january | october   |
| Cigar     | chaman          | game      | blend     | baccarat      |

