The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia, tulip, amaryllis
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 2. the person who growssunflower is not the fan of rock##6
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person playing domino and the person who growsdahlia##2
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
 6. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 8. the person driving the tram is the person who growstulip##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
11. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
13. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
14. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
15. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
17. the fan of rock is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
18. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
19. the person playing go is somewhere between the fan of country and the person eating asparagus##7
20. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
21. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
22. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
23. the person playing go is not the person watching spy movies##6
24. the person driving the quad-bike is between the fan of techno and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |      4       |
