The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, greysy, mystery, thriller
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, accountant, chef, bartender
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, malaysian, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, train, trike
 1. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 2. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
 3. the accountant is not the person watching thriller movies##6
 4. the japanese is somewhere between the mexican and the owner of the cat##7
 5. the bartender is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person who likes ivory##7
 7. the person eating apple is the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the person watching greysy movies is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 9. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
11. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
12. the owner of the fish is not the person who likes white##6
13. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
14. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
15. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
16. the person watching greysy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
17. the person driving the airplane is the accountant##1
18. the person watching greysy movies is in an odd position##4
19. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
20. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the dressmaker##1
21. the brazilian is not the bartender##6
22. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3     |      4       |
